1
00:00:01,020 --> 00:00:03,280
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:00:03,280 --> 00:00:04,480
Oh, no!

3
00:00:04,480 --> 00:00:07,770
Not only has Jellal been resurrected, 
but the seal on Nirvana has...

4
00:00:07,770 --> 00:00:09,100
...been released!

5
00:00:09,100 --> 00:00:11,270
We may have defeated one of Oracion Seis,

6
00:00:11,270 --> 00:00:14,200
but it seems like bad things 
are happening all around!

7
00:00:14,200 --> 00:00:16,650
And that's exactly why you 
can't get a boyfriend.

8
00:00:16,650 --> 00:00:19,370
H-Huh? What does that 
have to do with anything?

9
00:00:20,680 --> 00:00:28,670
If it's love and dreams and you it'll become magical.

10
00:00:28,670 --> 00:00:35,840
Now, let's cast a smile spell!

11
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:48,770
I kind of admired this powerful world,

12
00:00:48,770 --> 00:00:53,190
chock-full of problems.

13
00:00:54,110 --> 00:00:59,970
Frozen time has started to move again

14
00:00:59,970 --> 00:01:05,580
ever since I met you.

15
00:01:05,580 --> 00:01:11,000
Why were we born? Why do we live?

16
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:16,840
I don't need any complicated answers.

17
00:01:16,840 --> 00:01:22,780
Laugh! Cry! Be honest with yourself.

18
00:01:22,780 --> 00:01:27,560
Simple feelings are the most important.

19
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:35,900
You can change those tears shed on sad nights into strength.

20
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:42,530
Now, let's cast a smile spell!

21
00:01:53,510 --> 00:01:57,940
So basically, under that light, 
good and evil are switched, right?

22
00:01:57,940 --> 00:02:00,510
What'll we do? If Natsu turns into that...

23
00:02:01,050 --> 00:02:03,890
I don't care who, just come at me!

24
00:02:03,890 --> 00:02:07,320
I'll beat the crap outta you 
all, and destroy everything!

25
00:02:07,990 --> 00:02:09,520
Uh...

26
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:12,400
I think he might not be all that different...

27
00:02:12,650 --> 00:02:15,230
Guess good and evil don't 
really matter much to him.

28
00:02:15,480 --> 00:02:16,960
Anyway, we should hurry.

29
00:02:16,960 --> 00:02:19,110
We need to follow after 
Natsu-kun and Erza-san,

30
00:02:19,110 --> 00:02:21,870
and find some way to stop Nirvana!

31
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:31,830
Jellal! Your days are numbered!

32
00:02:31,830 --> 00:02:35,210
I ain't gonna let you get anywhere near Erza!

33
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,360
Spirit vs. Spirit!

34
00:02:44,940 --> 00:02:46,220
This smell...

35
00:02:50,260 --> 00:02:52,440
I knew it! Gray!

36
00:02:53,470 --> 00:02:56,150
What the hell are you doing here?

37
00:02:56,150 --> 00:02:58,000
What happened to the speedy one?

38
00:03:00,150 --> 00:03:01,120
Hey!

39
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:11,620
Damn it... I'm in a hurry here!

40
00:03:11,870 --> 00:03:13,370
Wake up, idiot!

41
00:03:15,750 --> 00:03:16,810
Gray...

42
00:03:20,960 --> 00:03:21,840
Gray?

43
00:03:28,760 --> 00:03:30,680
On a raft?!

44
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:36,480
Looks like you fell for it, Natsu.

45
00:03:36,740 --> 00:03:39,740
Your weak point really is "transportation."

46
00:03:41,540 --> 00:03:44,740
So how do you like the feeling of 
riding a raft bobbing up and down...

47
00:03:46,000 --> 00:03:48,150
You're... not...

48
00:03:48,150 --> 00:03:52,700
Shut up! Hurry up and kick the bucket, 
you slant-eyed, seasick bastard!

49
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:53,940
Or something like that...

50
00:03:53,940 --> 00:03:56,240
The usual battle between us two...

51
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,920
...ends today.

52
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:04,600
Who's there?

53
00:04:09,950 --> 00:04:11,610
What are you doing, Gray?

54
00:04:11,610 --> 00:04:13,280
It's us!

55
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:15,420
As it were, moshimoshi!

56
00:04:15,690 --> 00:04:18,190
L-Lucy...

57
00:04:19,870 --> 00:04:23,710
Would you try and refrain from 
hurling after saying my name?

58
00:04:23,710 --> 00:04:24,610
Moshimoshi.

59
00:04:24,610 --> 00:04:28,410
Anyway, that's horrible! 
You're going too far, Gray!

60
00:04:28,410 --> 00:04:31,490
Unless he stole your fish or 
something, then it's okay!

61
00:04:31,490 --> 00:04:33,360
Even then, I don't think so.

62
00:04:33,870 --> 00:04:35,870
Shut up, jerks.

63
00:04:35,870 --> 00:04:37,150
You're annoying.

64
00:04:37,150 --> 00:04:41,460
I'll get to you after I finish this 
guy off, so don't get in my way!

65
00:04:41,700 --> 00:04:42,580
Gray...

66
00:04:42,580 --> 00:04:46,400
W-What is this? Could Gray 
have fallen into the darkness?

67
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:47,480
It's...

68
00:04:50,740 --> 00:04:53,300
...swaying... swaying...

69
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:55,350
It's stopped, so get it together already!

70
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:57,650
Natsu, I'm coming to save you!

71
00:05:00,270 --> 00:05:01,300
He-cat!

72
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,780
Happy, what are you doing?

73
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:06,830
Happy can fly in the sky. 
He can carry one person.

74
00:05:06,830 --> 00:05:09,060
He has no offensive abilities.

75
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:11,360
Information gathering complete.

76
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:14,680
What are you saying, Gray? Wake up, already!

77
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:18,790
Is that how you become if you fall into 
darkness from Nirvana's influence?

78
00:05:19,180 --> 00:05:25,130
Lucy as seen by Gray: A newcomer to the 
guild. Looks are very much to his liking.

79
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:27,050
Somewhat interested in her.

80
00:05:27,650 --> 00:05:29,300
W-What the heck?

81
00:05:29,850 --> 00:05:33,660
More naive than at first glance. 
A Celestial Spirit Wizard.

82
00:05:34,410 --> 00:05:35,670
Spirits, eh?

83
00:05:36,490 --> 00:05:37,600
Interesting!

84
00:05:42,320 --> 00:05:45,580
No... You aren't Gray-kun.

85
00:05:45,580 --> 00:05:46,600
Who are you?

86
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:47,570
Not Gray?

87
00:05:47,820 --> 00:05:50,000
Hibiki as seen by Gray:

88
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:53,200
A member of Blue Pegasus. Handsome.

89
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,740
Doesn't know the details.

90
00:05:55,540 --> 00:05:57,050
Lack of information, huh?

91
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,800
He is acting strange, that's true.

92
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:03,750
Is this the effect of Nirvana?

93
00:06:03,750 --> 00:06:04,850
That's right...

94
00:06:04,850 --> 00:06:08,790
The people who fall into darkness are ones with
feelings in the gap between good and evil...

95
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:11,800
Gray isn't one to be moved so 
much by those kinds of feelings!

96
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,300
Who are you?

97
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:25,190
M-Me?

98
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:28,250
Are you dumb?

99
00:06:28,250 --> 00:06:32,950
Even if you transform into Lucy-san, 
you aren't going to fool us.

100
00:06:32,950 --> 00:06:37,120
I wonder about that. Men like you 
have a weak spot for women, yes?

101
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:45,050
Men...

102
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,970
B-Bobbing...

103
00:06:46,970 --> 00:06:48,200
Indeed!

104
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,550
Cut it out with the boob bobbing ogling!

105
00:06:50,550 --> 00:06:53,720
Honestly! What an uncouth wizard you are!

106
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:59,520
It's not me! It's that one! Although 
that's me! Argh, I don't know anymore!

107
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:03,040
Spirit information gathering complete.

108
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:06,340
Oh, wow! You have quite a lot of keys.

109
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:09,650
You've even had an audience 
with the Spirit King?

110
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:12,170
And your magical power isn't 
anything to laugh at either.

111
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:15,910
Well, whatever. Sagittarius?

112
00:07:16,760 --> 00:07:17,700
If you please...

113
00:07:19,640 --> 00:07:20,580
Moshimoshi?

114
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:24,690
Sagittarius?

115
00:07:24,690 --> 00:07:26,400
What is with this traitorous horse?

116
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:28,710
N-No, it's not me!

117
00:07:28,710 --> 00:07:31,800
I would never... do something like...

118
00:07:32,050 --> 00:07:33,820
Hibiki, hang in there!

119
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:37,680
Are you manipulating my Spirits?

120
00:07:37,930 --> 00:07:42,230
Yes! Right now, I can do everything you can.

121
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:46,250
I apologize, Lucy-dono, Hibiki-dono...

122
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:48,230
My body is moving on its own...

123
00:07:48,650 --> 00:07:52,610
Carla! Take Wendy and escape! 
This guy's dangerous!

124
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:57,490
I would even if you didn't tell me to!

125
00:07:57,740 --> 00:08:01,490
Sagittarius, I'm going to force your gate 
closed! You take a break for a while!

126
00:08:01,490 --> 00:08:04,070
I truly apologize, as it were. Moshimoshi.

127
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:09,800
In that case... Gate of 
the Archer, I open thee!

128
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,010
Sagittarius!

129
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:15,930
You called? Moshimoshi.

130
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:18,200
Uh, what?

131
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:21,250
What in the world is going on? Moshimoshi.

132
00:08:21,250 --> 00:08:23,310
I'm the one who summoned you.

133
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:26,680
So that means I'm your owner right now.

134
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:29,450
That is very true. Moshimoshi.

135
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:33,540
So with that settled, would you 
shoot down that flying cat for me?

136
00:08:34,350 --> 00:08:36,600
W-Well, I...

137
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,750
What is it?

138
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:40,540
Are you disobeying your owner?

139
00:08:41,560 --> 00:08:43,450
Even if your body and 
abilities are the same...

140
00:08:44,210 --> 00:08:47,860
You are not the real Lucy-dono!

141
00:08:47,860 --> 00:08:50,650
Even though I know this...

142
00:08:50,650 --> 00:08:52,270
Don't do it, Sagittarius!

143
00:08:52,270 --> 00:08:54,610
L-Lucy-dono...

144
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:55,930
Understood!

145
00:08:55,930 --> 00:08:58,400
Sagittarius, forced closure!

146
00:09:02,150 --> 00:09:05,060
Not gonna work. I summoned him, after all.

147
00:09:05,060 --> 00:09:07,520
Only I can do a forced closure.

148
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:08,820
But...

149
00:09:08,820 --> 00:09:11,550
Now, hurry up and shoot that cat!

150
00:09:13,050 --> 00:09:14,690
Oh, don't worry about her.

151
00:09:14,940 --> 00:09:20,650
Now that we've found Nirvana, 
that brat's role is over.

152
00:09:20,650 --> 00:09:21,890
Oh, I see!

153
00:09:22,530 --> 00:09:23,490
Sagittarius!

154
00:09:23,750 --> 00:09:27,330
Lucy-dono... Next time I'll 
be more helpful, really!

155
00:09:27,330 --> 00:09:28,920
Moshimoshi...

156
00:09:33,350 --> 00:09:35,100
Hi, Lucy-chan!

157
00:09:35,100 --> 00:09:37,380
Angel-chan is here!

158
00:09:37,690 --> 00:09:39,700
You're one of Oracion Seis!

159
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,580
Yup!

160
00:09:40,580 --> 00:09:46,140
And these guys can copy the body, powers,
and thoughts of their opponent completely!

161
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:47,630
I'm Gemi!

162
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:49,050
And I'm Mini!

163
00:09:49,410 --> 00:09:51,400
The Twin Spirits, Gemini.

164
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,820
I'm a Celestial Wizard too.

165
00:09:54,820 --> 00:09:58,170
A Celestial Wizard? Just like me...

166
00:09:58,900 --> 00:10:02,050
Just like it's not certain
that we'll fall into darkness,

167
00:10:02,050 --> 00:10:06,100
Oracion Seis isn't going to
turn good so easily either.

168
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:10,180
Right now, Nirvana's effect doesn't matter!

169
00:10:11,030 --> 00:10:14,410
Hibiki and Natsu can't fight.

170
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:16,750
I have to do something!

171
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:21,180
Thankfully, there's a 
stream here... with water!

172
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:25,600
I'd like those keys you have.

173
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:28,220
I'm going to wipe you out 
and take your Spirits.

174
00:10:28,220 --> 00:10:29,520
I won't let you do that!

175
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:32,100
Gate of the Water Bearer, I open thee!

176
00:10:32,340 --> 00:10:33,500
Gemini, gate closure.

177
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:36,120
Aquarius!

178
00:10:38,120 --> 00:10:41,240
Get her! I don't care 
if I get swept up in it!

179
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:43,150
That's what I was intending from the start.

180
00:10:43,610 --> 00:10:44,950
From the start?

181
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,980
I blow everyone away!

182
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:51,420
Gate of the Scorpion, I open thee!

183
00:10:51,420 --> 00:10:54,130
The Scorpion? That's one of the Zodiac!

184
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,920
Scorpio!

185
00:10:59,920 --> 00:11:03,090
We are! Yeah!

186
00:11:03,090 --> 00:11:04,910
Scorpio!

187
00:11:04,910 --> 00:11:06,450
What?!

188
00:11:06,450 --> 00:11:09,500
We are! How you been, Aquarius?

189
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:11,840
It's been a while, yeah!

190
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:15,010
I was so lonely! *sob-sob*

191
00:11:15,010 --> 00:11:18,070
Don't tell me... That 
boyfriend you talk about...

192
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:19,530
Yup! This is him!

193
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:21,290
We are!

194
00:11:21,290 --> 00:11:24,490
How do you do, Aquarius's owner?

195
00:11:24,490 --> 00:11:25,850
Yeah!

196
00:11:25,850 --> 00:11:29,000
Bam! And wait, what does this 
do to Aquarius's character?

197
00:11:29,590 --> 00:11:32,390
Just try saying something 
negative about my Scorpio...

198
00:11:32,390 --> 00:11:37,260
You ain't never gonna recover, you got it?

199
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,210
Yes.

200
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,460
She was totally serious!

201
00:11:40,460 --> 00:11:44,280
We are! There's a restaurant 
where we can see Aurora...

202
00:11:44,280 --> 00:11:47,250
So anyway, can I go back, Angel?

203
00:11:47,250 --> 00:11:48,100
Yeah...

204
00:11:48,350 --> 00:11:49,610
Go ahead!

205
00:11:50,390 --> 00:11:52,390
Aquarius, wait!

206
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:59,860
A little girl who doesn't even know about 
the relationship between Spirits...

207
00:12:00,690 --> 00:12:02,450
...can't beat me!

208
00:12:07,090 --> 00:12:11,160
What'll I do? My most powerful 
Spirit is blocked...

209
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:15,710
Wait! I have another one!

210
00:12:15,980 --> 00:12:18,010
The most powerful Spirit!

211
00:12:22,590 --> 00:12:24,180
Your prince has arrived.

212
00:12:24,180 --> 00:12:25,720
L-Leo?

213
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:28,620
Please! If you don't defeat 
her, then the guild will be...

214
00:12:28,620 --> 00:12:30,040
No sweat.

215
00:12:30,950 --> 00:12:32,980
Perhaps I didn't tell you?

216
00:12:32,980 --> 00:12:35,870
What's most important is the 
relationship between the Spirits.

217
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:38,190
Gate of the Ram, I open thee.

218
00:12:41,210 --> 00:12:42,400
Aries!

219
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,280
I'm sorry, Leo...

220
00:12:45,330 --> 00:12:46,600
Aries?

221
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,160
She was... Karen's...

222
00:12:49,740 --> 00:12:52,630
Karen's Spirit Aries...

223
00:12:52,630 --> 00:12:53,830
Why is she here?

224
00:12:54,380 --> 00:12:57,110
Loke can't fight like this!

225
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:08,540
Aries...

226
00:13:09,800 --> 00:13:11,450
Karen's Spirit?

227
00:13:12,050 --> 00:13:14,440
Why do you have Karen's Spirit?

228
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:17,190
Because I'm the one that offed her!

229
00:13:19,110 --> 00:13:21,700
This here is just the spoils of battle.

230
00:13:22,130 --> 00:13:23,530
I'm sorry!

231
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:27,190
Even though that woman didn't 
have much magic power,

232
00:13:27,190 --> 00:13:30,400
she tried to force a simultaneous 
release of two spirits.

233
00:13:30,400 --> 00:13:31,990
She did herself in.

234
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:35,510
Although I was the one that finished her off.

235
00:13:37,250 --> 00:13:41,930
I've taken the keys of all kinds of 
Celestial Wizards that I've wiped out.

236
00:13:42,790 --> 00:13:46,750
I'm also gonna take those Spirits you use.

237
00:13:48,050 --> 00:13:49,120
Karen...

238
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:52,570
Karen... This woman did it...

239
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:58,130
To my... beloved...

240
00:13:59,100 --> 00:14:01,000
It was you...

241
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,800
You Celestial Wizard...

242
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:07,850
You...

243
00:14:08,660 --> 00:14:11,850
It was your fault...

244
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:16,210
No! I'm being consumed by hatred!

245
00:14:16,210 --> 00:14:18,110
My heart is going to be stolen by Nirvana!

246
00:14:18,110 --> 00:14:19,920
I'm falling into darkness!

247
00:14:20,430 --> 00:14:22,440
I can't think like that!

248
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:27,380
You finally meet again, but as enemies?

249
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:31,370
Loke, go back to your world.

250
00:14:31,370 --> 00:14:33,310
Don't think so little of me, Lucy.

251
00:14:34,010 --> 00:14:38,390
Even if we were once friends, with 
different owners, we are now enemies.

252
00:14:39,490 --> 00:14:41,980
Spirits fight for their masters.

253
00:14:42,760 --> 00:14:45,180
Even if it's against someone 
they have feelings for,

254
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:47,280
we will defeat the enemy for our master!

255
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,610
That is our...

256
00:14:53,050 --> 00:14:54,450
...pride!

257
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:57,450
Oh, no...

258
00:15:01,790 --> 00:15:04,560
Oh? They're going at it?

259
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:08,380
Well, this is interesting 
in its own way, so go ahead.

260
00:15:08,770 --> 00:15:09,880
No...

261
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:17,670
This... This... isn't right!

262
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:20,180
Wool Bomb!

263
00:15:27,590 --> 00:15:29,850
As expected from the leader of the Zodiacs...

264
00:15:29,850 --> 00:15:33,160
She's no match for Leo, the Spirit 
specializing in battle, I guess.

265
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,690
Well, in that case...

266
00:15:35,690 --> 00:15:38,400
Gate of the the Chisel, I open thee!

267
00:15:39,940 --> 00:15:40,750
Caelum!

268
00:15:43,830 --> 00:15:46,700
Okay, Caelum, target.

269
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:50,550
Aim for when Aries stops Leo's movement!

270
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:09,090
That worked great!

271
00:16:09,090 --> 00:16:10,260
Leo!

272
00:16:10,260 --> 00:16:11,440
Aries...

273
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:14,630
I'm sorry, Lucy...

274
00:16:15,610 --> 00:16:20,660
I'm glad you met a nice owner...

275
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:29,560
So how do you like my simultaneous release?

276
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:33,890
I don't think you'll be using 
your powerhouse Leo anytime soon.

277
00:16:35,100 --> 00:16:36,750
I can't believe you...

278
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:42,050
What? It's not like Spirits die 
anyway, so what's the big deal?

279
00:16:42,050 --> 00:16:44,240
But they feel pain!

280
00:16:44,750 --> 00:16:46,700
They have feelings!

281
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:49,270
And yet you call yourself a Celestial Wizard?

282
00:16:51,670 --> 00:16:54,190
Gate of the Bull, I open thee!

283
00:16:55,280 --> 00:16:55,860
Taurus!

284
00:16:59,650 --> 00:17:00,530
Gemini!

285
00:17:02,130 --> 00:17:07,210
I don't care who it is, if you make 
my Nice Body cry, I won't forgive you!

286
00:17:08,880 --> 00:17:11,210
Come here, Moo-moo-chan!

287
00:17:11,210 --> 00:17:13,670
Lucy-san!

288
00:17:14,260 --> 00:17:15,860
And another one bites the dust!

289
00:17:15,860 --> 00:17:17,260
Mooore!

290
00:17:17,260 --> 00:17:18,260
Taurus!

291
00:17:21,060 --> 00:17:22,790
Huh? Why am I...

292
00:17:23,640 --> 00:17:28,420
You can't use so many Spirits like that 
without a huge amount of magical power.

293
00:17:28,730 --> 00:17:30,270
But...

294
00:17:35,600 --> 00:17:39,060
Literally bringing defeat 
upon herself... What a dope!

295
00:17:46,800 --> 00:17:48,500
Serves you right!

296
00:17:49,780 --> 00:17:51,490
Serves you right...

297
00:18:02,050 --> 00:18:04,710
What's that look for? I don't like it.

298
00:18:04,710 --> 00:18:07,190
Release Aries from her contract!

299
00:18:07,190 --> 00:18:09,000
Huh? What?

300
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,960
She was abused by her previous owner.

301
00:18:13,610 --> 00:18:16,120
And went through nothing but hardships...

302
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:17,900
So...

303
00:18:25,370 --> 00:18:30,190
And what do people say when they 
ask for favors again, Lucy-chan?

304
00:18:34,410 --> 00:18:37,560
P-Please...

305
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:44,000
I want to let Aries and Loke be together!

306
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:49,580
It's we Celestial Wizards who are the 
only ones who can do that for them!

307
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,200
For free?

308
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,820
I'll give you anything.

309
00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:59,320
Other than my keys, I'll give you anything!

310
00:19:01,280 --> 00:19:03,320
Then that would be your life.

311
00:19:03,640 --> 00:19:05,310
Gemini, do it!

312
00:19:12,930 --> 00:19:14,040
Gemini?

313
00:19:15,850 --> 00:19:19,560
Her beautiful voice... resounds...

314
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:22,750
Mama, Mama!

315
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:25,530
I love Spirits!

316
00:19:25,530 --> 00:19:27,570
Spirits aren't shields!

317
00:19:27,930 --> 00:19:31,730
I can't just let my friend 
disappear in front of my eyes!

318
00:19:34,540 --> 00:19:36,490
I can't do it...

319
00:19:38,890 --> 00:19:40,430
Lucy...

320
00:19:40,430 --> 00:19:42,630
...loves them from her heart.

321
00:19:43,050 --> 00:19:45,320
She loves us Spirits!

322
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:49,230
Gemini...

323
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:50,990
Begone!

324
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:55,910
How useless!

325
00:20:06,810 --> 00:20:07,860
Hibiki?

326
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:12,260
Wait, did the cool one fall into darkness?

327
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:16,010
Hold still.

328
00:20:17,950 --> 00:20:25,780
My magic, Archive, is going to give you the 
knowledge of a super powerful spell, just this once!

329
00:20:35,080 --> 00:20:36,750
What is this?

330
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:38,800
Inside... my head...

331
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:41,130
Figures I don't understand!

332
00:20:41,630 --> 00:20:47,010
That was close... I almost 
fell into darkness.

333
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:52,710
But the bonds you have with your 
Spirits wrapped me in the light.

334
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:56,350
I know you'll be able to use this magic!

335
00:20:56,810 --> 00:20:59,100
Damn you! Caelum!

336
00:21:06,290 --> 00:21:08,880
I'm counting on you, Lucy!

337
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:18,050
Measure heaven, open heaven.

338
00:21:18,050 --> 00:21:22,710
Make unto my body as to shine with
the radiance of the countless stars.

339
00:21:22,710 --> 00:21:26,150
Tetra Biblos, I am the ruler of the stars.

340
00:21:26,150 --> 00:21:29,890
Aspect, cast open the 
gate of perfect malevolence...

341
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:34,480
What is this? Caelum, hurry!

342
00:21:35,060 --> 00:21:37,350
The 88 Stars of the Heavens.

343
00:21:38,960 --> 00:21:40,110
Shine!

344
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:42,100
Urano Meteoria!

345
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:12,640
Huh?

346
00:22:13,330 --> 00:22:15,400
I figured you'd be able to do it.

347
00:22:16,550 --> 00:22:18,160
Urano Meteoria...

348
00:23:55,700 --> 00:23:58,860
I thought I blew Jellal away 
at the Tower of Heaven...

349
00:23:58,860 --> 00:24:00,400
Why is he here again?

350
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:01,770
He must be a ghost!

351
00:24:01,770 --> 00:24:03,600
And he's come back for revenge!

352
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,240
Ghosts can't use magic!

353
00:24:05,240 --> 00:24:06,880
Then maybe he's an identical twin?

354
00:24:06,880 --> 00:24:10,340
Don't you remember? The twin 
was a fake he made with magic.

355
00:24:10,340 --> 00:24:13,420
A cat's brain can't think of anything else.

356
00:24:14,180 --> 00:24:16,430
Next time: Recollections of Jellal.

357
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:18,890
Can't go relying on your 
brain, can we, Happy?

358
00:24:18,890 --> 00:24:22,470
Although I think I'm way 
smarter than you, Natsu!

359
00:24:22,470 --> 00:24:23,900
Say what?!

360
00:24:23,900 --> 00:24:26,150


